{"sections":{"main":{"type":"main-page","disabled":true,"settings":{"narrow":true,"padding_top":60,"padding_bottom":72}},"bf506bfa-0c8b-403b-8e13-27ec35e10efd":{"type":"images-with-text","blocks":{"template--14887843201066__bf506bfa-0c8b-403b-8e13-27ec35e10efd-1675799451802a7fc7-0":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"Our Classic and Reserve Collections are made to be mixed, matched, and layered together.","heading_size":"h2","heading_tag":"h2"}},"98a19e9d-a8cf-4550-b0a1-17f7b716e452":{"type":"subheading","settings":{"subheading":"What is layering?","subheading_size":"h4","secondary_color":false}},"8880c60e-3b01-4c10-841a-52d317923eb2":{"type":"heading","disabled":true,"settings":{"heading":"What is layering?","heading_size":"h2","heading_tag":"h2"}},"template--14887843201066__bf506bfa-0c8b-403b-8e13-27ec35e10efd-1675799451802a7fc7-1":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>Layering is the art of creating your own personalized scent by combining two or more fragrances. At Clean Beauty Collective, we encourage you to layer our different fragrances to create an altogether new scent totally unique to you.<\/p><p><\/p><p>Get started by mixing your favorite Clean Beauty Collective scents. This is the fun part—so experiment generously. Though we recommend doing so first on a sheet of paper. When you find one that strikes your fancy, pair it and apply to your skin.<\/p>","text_size":"typeset2","secondary_color":false}}},"block_order":["template--14887843201066__bf506bfa-0c8b-403b-8e13-27ec35e10efd-1675799451802a7fc7-0","98a19e9d-a8cf-4550-b0a1-17f7b716e452","8880c60e-3b01-4c10-841a-52d317923eb2","template--14887843201066__bf506bfa-0c8b-403b-8e13-27ec35e10efd-1675799451802a7fc7-1"],"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/34_Sparklingsugar_Joy_125.jpg","image_2":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Shot_60_CR_Pairing_Shot_Shot_60_CR_Pairing_Shot_1564_square_9169db70-2a47-4c4f-a8ec-7f6d14e4e473.jpg","image_3":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Shot55_CCSpringGiftSetLS_Shot55_CCSpringGift